{"tid":2324482,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"wfh壞處","createTime":"2020-12-14T03:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T08:57:38.000Z","uid":384364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"33539372a0779b4b057299e17bf4b857bdd12bab","tid":2324482,"uid":384364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:29:30.000Z","msg":"本身同公司講咗去過確診餐廳<br />\n公司第一日都照要我翻工等消息睇吓洗唔洗隔離<br />\n臨收工前即刻要我拎電腦翻屋企wfh <br />\n之後就算我拎漏嘢都已經唔再俾我翻上公司攞<br />\n<br />\n過多兩日後<br />\n我開始咳、發燒、不停嘔同喉嚨痛<br />\n連續請咗兩日假 + 星期六日 <br />\n去咗做深喉唾液檢測 <br />\n依家仲等緊結果 <br />\n<br />\n去到今日<br />\n我仲咳緊同想嘔<br />\n但係因為我人唔喺公司<br />\n已經無人會理你係咪確診或者有咩病徵<br />\n<br />\nWfh係咪就代表你幾病都要繼續翻工？<br />\n因為你已經唔會傳染俾啲同事 <br />\n就算本身份工要不停對客講嘢<br />\n只要你唔係失聲你都要繼續翻工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e9ec002b00917594bd7ed5ee0f5cc16e8badf5","tid":2324482,"uid":2950,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDy5sth.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDy5sth.gif&h=d4dc8aea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Dq3YAj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Dq3YAj.gif&h=292a6c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1WyBm3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1WyBm3.gif&h=c8e7bb14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Hpkgm7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Hpkgm7.gif&h=d7fa4459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用電腦傳染班同事"},{"pid":"3f2e1f2b14d3fb59e459933fe07b393bee39c2e7","tid":2324482,"uid":300352,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"關咩wfh事<br />\n有病就睇醫生請病假係常識<br />\n唔洗拋個病樣俾上司同事睇<br />\n佢地有咩專業資格話你既健康狀況返唔返到工？<br />\n你請病假既權力係勞工法同醫生俾你<br />\n唔係你公司、上司或同事"},{"pid":"faf9a9459f2d17f61a3a700e94419b34853b350a","tid":2324482,"uid":77320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:52:26.000Z","msg":"懷疑你係咪我同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84bc7845b3015bb51112d0d6d5e7d5ef3db25370","tid":2324482,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:16:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3f93cbd7b51c6ad1094b955c220af2630c3ef8f","tid":2324482,"uid":77320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:30:06.000Z","msg":"好老實講我覺得呢個疫情真係冇令大家close咗囉<br />\n咩同屋企人見面時間多咗真係得啖笑<br />\n見面時間多咗咪即係磨擦多咗囉<br />\nWfh嘅壞處樓主已經講咗"},{"pid":"971268819092e97adfb14cb50d355c803393be9f","tid":2324482,"uid":243988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"其實明唔明WFH 點解?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病就唔好返工, 響屋企休息"},{"pid":"f0677b4f1eeb62ed124f7650cba380e158fbbd6f","tid":2324482,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"戇鳩？<br />\nWFH 都可以請病假架...<br />\n不過啲19HR應該好麻煩"},{"pid":"70cb898b48f02c589216b2fb9bc807eb64114653","tid":2324482,"uid":70888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c3e9ec002b00917594bd7ed5ee0f5cc16e8badf5","tid":2324482,"uid":2950,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T03:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDy5sth.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDy5sth.gif&h=d4dc8aea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Dq3YAj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Dq3YAj.gif&h=292a6c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1WyBm3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1WyBm3.gif&h=c8e7bb14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Hpkgm7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Hpkgm7.gif&h=d7fa4459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用電腦傳染班同事"},"